  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This award strives to generate rapid, sustained, and broad-based economic growth. More specifically, this includes a BUSLAB provides innovative transport solutions in Polokwane City. It aims at closing the gap by being an active lead supplier of alternative transport to people in the community. The company&#x2019;s strategy is to build a reputable market share by offering shared taxi as a viable alternative to existing taxicab services. BUSLAB will provide 3-wheeler&#x2019;s Tuk-Tuk transport services utilizing computer dispatch to help with timely pick up and quality customer care. The software and hardware systems that will be used will give customers convenience by allowing them to use credit and debit cards in the taxi..</narrative>
  </description>
